                            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">
                                Predictive Insights
                            </h3>
                            <ul class="text-gray-400 space-y-2 text-sm">
                                <li>
                                    • <strong>Capacity Planning:</strong> Predice
                                    necesidades de recursos
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    • <strong>Performance Forecasting:</strong> Anticipa
                                    degradación
