                            Performance Optimization
                        </h3>
                        <ul class="text-gray-400 space-y-2 text-sm">
                            <li>• Bottleneck identification</li>
                            <li>• Resource optimization</li>
                            <li>• Code-level insights</li>
                            <li>• Database query analysis</li>
