                                        Detecta anomalía en pricing service
                                        (latencia +300%)
                                    </li>
                                    <li>
                                        Mapea dependencies: 12 services
                                        downstream
                                    </li>
                                    <li>
                                        Predice impacto: checkout process en
                                        riesgo
                                    </li>
                                    <li>
                                        Identifica root cause: database
                                        connection pool exhausted
                                    </li>
                                </ol>
                            </div>

                            <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-4">
                                <div class="text-xs text-gray-400 mb-2">
                                    Davis Alert & Analysis
                                </div>
                                <pre
                                    class="text-xs text-purple-400"><code>{`🚨 CRITICAL ALERT
Service: pricing-service-v2
Impact: HIGH (Revenue at risk)

Timeline:
14:23 - Latency spike detected (+300%)
14:24 - Root cause identified: DB connection pool
14:24 - Downstream impact predicted
14:25 - Auto-scaling recommendation generated

Causal Chain:
┌─ pricing-service-v2 ─────────────┐
│  Database Connection Pool (8/8)  │ ← ROOT CAUSE
│  └─ High query volume            │
│     └─ Black Friday traffic      │
└──────────────────────────────────┘
         ↓ IMPACTS ↓
┌─ cart-service ───┐  ┌─ checkout-service ─┐
│ Timeout errors   │  │ Failed purchases   │
│ 15% failure rate │  │ Revenue loss: $2M/h│
└──────────────────┘  └────────────────────┘

RECOMMENDED ACTIONS:
1. 🔧 Scale DB connection pool (8→32)
2. ⚡ Enable read replicas
3. 🔄 Activate circuit breaker
4. 📊 Monitor checkout conversion`}</code></pre>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div
                        class="bg-gray-900 rounded-xl p-8 border border-indigo-500/20"
                    >
                        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-6">
                            🔮 Predictive Capacity Planning
                        </h3>

                        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
